description: Lost Robot is a only physics-based puzzle game that combines the concepts of the gravity, friction and Three Laws of Motions. It is an ideal app for kids to interactively learn the Physics and still have fun.The story begins many years in the future. A genius professor invents a new super robot. The robot can recharge itself from absorbing energy from the stars in space. And it will never die. The professor gives the robot to his daughter as a gift. The little girl has a dream to see the beautiful flowers from the ancient age. The robot remembers her wish and starts the journey to look for the flowers in the sky far, far away.Key Features:â€¢5 chapters with 60 levels (more to come)â€¢Innovative physics game playâ€¢Simulation of realistic physics environment â€“ Three Laws of Motion, gravity, and frictionâ€¢Perfect supplemental tool for your kid to learn basic physics.â€¢Multiple solutions to solve the same puzzle.â€¢Complete control of gravity and friction via touch buttonsâ€¢Help system that can assist you with the puzzleâ€¢Global high scores â€¢Adorable character and beautiful background graphicsâ€¢Optimized for both phones and tablets
name: Lost Robot - A Physics Puzzler

description: Available languages: English - French - Italian - German - Swedish - Dutch - Spanish - Polish - Czech - Portuguese Note: Please note, this game is made especially for tiny.
